<br>
my left hand is using the A,S,D,W keys for forward and backward.  When you click on the right mouse button and turn you strafe with your 'A' and 'W' keys.  Also with my left hand I have Backstab on the #2 key and disarm on my #3 key.<br>
<br>
Having a fast connection helps as well. But, you must always be moving and just act like your a fly determined to land on the moving dog poop.  <br>
<br>
It is even more irritating when your victim begins to run.  I could be on him the entire run, but I will not hit him due to some lag.  The best attack from a rogue, is when your victim is not expecting it and your able to hit him with a blind or snare poison so he cannot run off.  Otherwise I just avoid most other Melee PvP.<br>
<br>
<br>
Good Luck<br>
